com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport

Class SearchResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport.SearchResults

  • public final class SearchResults
extends Object
    Contains the Items and ItemSearchResults that form the results of a search operation.

    The Items include all matching Entitys and Links, plus the Entitys at the ends of the Links. No Item appears more than once.

    Each ItemSearchResult has a corresponding Item, unless this SearchResults refers to a set whose contents are not visible.

    Since:
    1.0
